 />\n<br />\n廣東歌已經較華語歌失去很大競爭優勢及市場份額<br />\n<br />\n如果歌詞並非以現代標準漢語的白話文規範去寫<br />\n<br />\n即是其他地區的人連閱讀書面的歌詞都難以理解<br />\n<br />\n就更難推廣、宣傳<br />\n<br />\n況於今粵語用字、辭彙、詞藻未有公認標準<br />\n<br />\n粵語文學亦沉痾難起<br />\n<br />\n故刻下貼近粵語口頭格式的歌詞難以不被大衆視爲流俗</blockquote><br />\n但Sam Hui啲歌喺全球華人圈入面都好hit喎<br />\n好似&ldquo;財神到&rdquo;咁，華人社區一到新年一定會播，咪一樣有用口語去寫，都唔會話要譯返書面語先識聽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋如果淨係填一兩隻口語字落去都唔會好影響個字面意思啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSam Hui 嗰時 香港lead 住亞洲文化喎</blockquote><br />\n我只係講對於歌詞理解上嘅問題啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069749e032023081e79c8afd2e0877bf3d8054e8","tid":179688,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T12:42:37.000Z","msg":"2002年，黃偉文與伍樂城合作進行了一個提倡「以廣東口語入詞」的寫詞運動&nbsp;...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cantonpopblog.blogspot.hk/2012/04/blog-post_4598.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcantonpopblog.blogspot.hk%2F2012%2F04%2Fblog-post_4598.html%3Fm%3D1&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAY2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=0c678a6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://cantonpopblog.blogspot.hk/2012/04/blog-post_4598.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"c71c6dbcbcbbbfaf3b95e97050f64b9ca481a0a7","tid":179688,"uid":59773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T12:47:49.000Z","msg":"尹光果d數波波，數毛毛，相士大隻西算唔算？"},{"pid":"7f12114ea25220efe879c82cef5c7e45f79b74b0","tid":179688,"uid":66909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:08:55.000Z","msg":"強帖黎明"},{"pid":"f1f00ebbe3b66a83afd18daf932a3d0de4d86339","tid":179688,"uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:59:50.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\nbtw 如果係全口語冇乜問題 但如果前果幾句用左乜乜是乜乜之類 後面又出 係 呢d唔咸唔淡真係幾肉酸"},{"pid":"507d721b62fda1f432534b5165b48983ed2b90d9","tid":179688,"uid":66909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T02:48:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm<